"title": "8223: dedication",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8223: dedication",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The single-minded devoting of a person, object or action to the honour of God.</p>\n<h2>Personal dedication to God must be wholehearted</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:5\">JOS 22:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:20\">DEU 10:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:14-Josh24:15\">JOS 24:14–24:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:9\">1CH 28:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh10:28-Neh10:29\">NEH 10:28–10:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:106\">PSA 119:106</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:37\">MAT 22:37</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:30\">MRK 12:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:27\">LUK 10:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:5\">DEU 6:5</a></p>\n<h2>OT dedication to the worship and service of God</h2>\n<h3>Dedication of individuals</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:1-Num6:8\">NUM 6:1–6:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:5\">JDG 13:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:7\">JDG 13:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:17\">JDG 16:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:11\">1SA 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:25\">PRO 20:25</a></p>\n<h3>Dedication of property</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev27:1-Lev27:8\">LEV 27:1–27:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev27:9-Lev27:27\">LEV 27:9–27:27</a></p>\n<h3>Dedication of animals</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev1:1-Lev1:4\">LEV 1:1–1:4</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Dedication of the priesthood</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num18:6\">NUM 18:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:41\">EXO 28:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev21:10-Lev21:12\">LEV 21:10–21:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:8\">DEU 10:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:2\">1CH 15:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr23:13\">1CH 23:13</a></p>\n<h3>Dedication of the tabernacle and its furnishings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:1\">NUM 7:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:10\">NUM 7:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:84\">NUM 7:84</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:88\">NUM 7:88</a></p>\n<h3>Dedication of the temple and its contents</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:51\">1KI 7:51</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:1\">2CH 5:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:63-1Kgs8:64\">1KI 8:63–8:64</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:15\">1KI 15:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:4\">2CH 2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:9\">2CH 7:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra6:16-Ezra6:18\">EZR 6:16–6:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:5\">LUK 21:5</a></p>\n<h3>Dedication of particular items of value</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:51\">1KI 7:51</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:1\">2CH 5:1</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:15\">1KI 15:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:1-1Chr29:5\">1CH 29:1–29:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:6\">2CH 3:6</a></p>\n<h3>Dedication of the booty of war</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam8:11-2Sam8:12\">2SA 8:11–8:12</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr18:11\">1CH 18:11</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:28\">NUM 31:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:19\">JOS 6:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:1\">JOS 7:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:10-Josh7:13\">JOS 7:10–7:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr26:27\">1CH 26:27</a></p>\n<h2>NT dedication to God and his service</h2>\n<h3>Dedication is more usually applied to people than things</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1\">ROM 12:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:24\">MAT 6:24</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:13\">LUK 16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:29\">MAT 19:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:36-Acts4:37\">ACT 4:36–4:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:13\">ROM 6:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:16\">ROM 6:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:19\">ROM 6:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:1-1Cor16:2\">1CO 16:1–16:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:11\">1TI 5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:15-1Pet1:16\">1PE 1:15–1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:44\">LEV 11:44</a></p>\n<h3>Particular work and time may be given over to the service of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:1-Acts6:4\">ACT 6:1–6:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:14\">ACT 1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:2\">ACT 13:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:1\">ROM 1:1</a></p>\n<h3>Service for others is to be dedicated to God and done in his name</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:17\">COL 3:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:31\">1CO 10:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:21\">EPH 5:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:5-Eph6:7\">EPH 6:5–6:7</a></p>",
